name: Supersonic: North America's Tribute To Oasis
venue_name: The Pearl Showroom, Pure Casino Yellowhead
description: Formed in 2009, SuperSonic is a talented lineup of musicians who share a passion for the music of Oasis. Each performer captures the essence of the band, ensuring that every show is a true homage to their legendary sound. The energy they bring to those iconic tracks--Live Forever, Supersonic, Wonderwall, Don't Look Back In Anger, Champagne Supernova and more creates an unforgettable atmosphere. Join us in the Pearl Showroom for dinner & drink service right at your seat!

name: The HIP Experience: Celebrating the music of The Tragically Hip
venue_name: The Pearl Showroom, Pure Casino Yellowhead
description: The HIP Experience was formed in 2017 shortly after the passing of Gord Downie in October of that year. The band was originally put together for a memorial tribute concert to the Canadian Icon. The Hip Experience is a crowd favourite at festivals with their high energy delivery of the Tragically Hips music. The bands performances capture the spirit of the Hip with great attention to detail and the nuances of the music. Join us in the Pearl Showroom for dinner & drink service right at your seat!
